{"tid":1420281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宜家就回應你條玉石俱焚","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:23:08.000Z","uid":168457,"like":158,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"65ce49f80c7977c7a7c64d0f5dab372ad2f71226","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:12:19.000Z","msg":"香港社會會否去到玉石俱焚既主導權並唔喺示威者手上，只要香港政府能夠懸崖勒馬，正面回應示威者缺一不可嘅五大訴求，香港社會一定可以重回繁榮穩定嘅軌道。<br />\n<br />\n但假若港共政府繼續一意孤行，我對香港人好有信心。縱使玉石俱焚，香港定能浴火重生！<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1fe20bb3bc1eb6e86fffadf2c37224c92e8f5955","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"2f855c1b42f055ff425ea017df5b965633aeb03b","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"45b1f6a6dd4f5807fee82f8d1f72c4520cdbd408","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"941678058c933bd0e0b4b87529e5fd09c0b6640f","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"3fa6f40671c980c6bb5f57cf9f90ad5410f4510b","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"8a25c508efc4974d3bcaf473d9c66c0700799c3f","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"092a0dc2596cf5919fa2d4253b33545fe624f89b","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"9a6ee670626c645ab814e92763374823190652a0","tid":1420281,"uid":168457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"61488fd5a39889a8ec3cfa